<template>
  <vBasePage :searchOptions="searchOptions" :tableOption="tableOption" @rowBlock="rowClick"></vBasePage>
</template>

<script>
import vBasePage from "../../BasePage/BasePage";
import FileManagerApi from "../webapi/FileManager";
import moment from "moment";
import config from "@/config/index";
import { FileType } from '../js/FileType';

export default {
  data() {
    let formatter = function(val, row) {
      return moment(val).format("YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm");
    };
    return {
      searchOptions: {
        searchOptions: {
          requiredCondition: false
        },
        seleFunc: {
          export: false,
          search: true
        },
        search_controls: [
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "仓库编号",
            key: "PlaceId"
          },
          {
            type: "v_text",
            title: "采集器枪号",
            key: "EquipmentNumber"
          },
          {
            type: "v_datetime",
            title: "上传开始日期",
            key: "UpdateTimeStartDate"
            //defdate: moment(new Date()).add(-1, 'months').format("YYYY-MM-DD")
          },
          {
            type: "v_datetime",
            title: "上传结束日期",
            key: "UpdateTimeEndDate"
          }
        ]
      },
      tableOption: {
        tableId: "pushabnormal",
        tableName: "物流文件上传文件日志",
        url:
          config.pgyerApiUrl +
          FileManagerApi.GetLogisticsFileUploadLogList.options.url,
        method: FileManagerApi.GetLogisticsFileUploadLogList.options.method,
        columns: [
          {
            field: "placeId",
            title: "仓库编号",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "equipmentNumber",
            title: "枪号",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "createTime",
            title: "文件上传日",
            align: "center",
            formatter: formatter
          },
          {
            field: "fileName",
            title: "文件名",
            align: "center",
            width: "150px"
          },
          {
            field: "fileType",
            title: "文件类型",
            align: "center",
            formatter: function(val, row) {
              return FileType[row.fileType];
            }
          },
          {
            field: "clientIp",
            title: "客户端IP地址",
            align: "center"
          },

          {
            field: "systemVersion",
            title: "系统版本号",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "operatingSystemType",
            title: "操作系统类型",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "operatingSystemVersion",
            title: "操作系统版本号",
            align: "center"
          },
          {
            field: "updateTime",
            title: "文件生成时间",
            align: "center",
            formatter: formatter
          }
        ]
      }
    };
  },
  methods: {
    rowClick: function(rowItem, element, baseObject) {
      console.log(element);
      debugger;
    }
  },
  components: { vBasePage }
};
</script>
